Get sorted array of serial ports in the system using default settings:
Search path
Windows - ""(always ignored)
Linux - "/dev/"
Solaris - "/dev/term/"
MacOSX - "/dev/"
RegExp
Windows - ""
Linux - "(ttyS|ttyUSB|ttyACM|ttyAMA|rfcomm)[0-9]{1,3}"
Solaris - "[0-9]*|[a-z]*"
MacOSX - "tty.
